messages.message: Hi, who owns the Document Diff app that is referenced in the documentation here (https://instabase.com/docs/reference/apps/document-diff/)? It looks different from the Diff Checker app but cannot find the app itself or any additional information. Bank of America is asking about it so I want to make sure to set the right expectations (CC: @Kristine, @Blaise )

@Kristine @Bren Document Diff app is deprecated a while back and was removed. Seems like the documentation is not updated. Diff Checker is the only available app now to view text differences. Will take care of removing (https://instabase.atlassian.net/browse/DR-693) this from the documentation.
